PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775596265
OL,3,CFamily of man who died outside
OL,4,CBournemouth bar 'utterly heartbroken'
OL,6,F"He was the most incredible, lovable
OL,7,Fhuman that lit up any room with his
OL,8,Fmassive smile.
OL,10,F"He was not just my husband but an
OL,11,Fincredible father to our two beautiful
OL,12,Fchildren who are heartbroken beyond
OL,13,Fbelief.
OL,15,F"My James was an amazing husband,
OL,16,Ffather son, brother, uncle and friend.
OL,17,FHe was the most loyal person who would
OL,18,Fdo anything for anyone.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775596265
OL,3,CFamily of man who died outside
OL,4,CBournemouth bar 'utterly heartbroken'
OL,6,F"James would just make everything
OL,7,Fbetter and always tell you that 'it's
OL,8,Fgoing to be alright'.
OL,10,F"Everything he did was for his two
OL,11,Fchildren who he loved more than
OL,12,Fanything in the world. I am forever
OL,13,Fgrateful for our 18 years together and
OL,14,FI will continue to make you proud with
OL,15,Four two children.
OL,17,F"We are all utterly heartbroken and
OL,18,Fnothing will ever feel the same again.
OL,20,F"We love you James, daddy, today,
OL,21,Ftomorrow and forever.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU|D@AOU
